        <abstract>
            <p>Dr Hooker has given him CD’s memorandum on the fly-catcher.</p> 
<p>Copies out extract from <hi rend="italic">Curtis’ Botanical Magazine</hi> [On <hi rend="italic">Apocynum androsæmifolium</hi>, 8 (1794): tab.]: 280 and gives a further reference in Erasmus Darwin’s <hi rend="italic">The loves of plants</hi> [1789]. Suggests that they look at <hi rend="italic">Apocynum</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
